    <item>
      <title>印度卡车司机罢工威胁食品、燃料和物资供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/india-truckers-strike-threatens-food-fuel-goods-supplies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度各地的卡车司机参加了全国范围内的罢工，反对一项新法律，该法律对肇事逃逸犯罪实施更严厉的惩罚，导致货物供应延误并引发燃料短缺的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-02/india-truckers-strike-threatens-food-fuel-goods-supplies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 13:40:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
